Who we areAbout NBCUniversalWe are one of the world’s leading media and entertainment companies in the development, production, and marketing of entertainment, news and information to a global audience.NBCUniversal owns and operates a valuable portfolio of news and entertainment television networks, a premier motion picture company, significant television production operations, a leading television stations group, world-renowned theme parks, and a suite of leading Internet-based businesses. NBCUniversal is a subsidiary of Comcast Corporation.





